name: Nostromo 1.9.6 Directory Traversal / Remote code execution
service: status:open - protocol:http - name:webserver - summary:(80/http) webserver (1.9.6) - version:1.9.6 - ports:80
desc: Directory Traversal in the function http_verify in nostromo nhttpd through 1.9.6 allows an attacker to achieve remote code execution via a crafted HTTP request.
resolution: Upgrade nostromo webserver to a version after 1.9.6.
